40SmartScript::SmartScript()
41{
42 go = NULL;
43 me = NULL;
44 trigger = NULL;
45 mEventPhase = 0;
46 mPathId = 0;
47 mTargetStorage = new ObjectListMap();
48 mTextTimer = 0;
49 mLastTextID = 0;
50 mUseTextTimer = false;
51 mTalkerEntry = 0;
52 mTemplate = SMARTAI_TEMPLATE_BASIC;
53 mScriptType = SMART_SCRIPT_TYPE_CREATURE;
54 isProcessingTimedActionList = false;
55}
56
57SmartScript::~SmartScript()
58{
59 for (ObjectListMap::iterator itr = mTargetStorage->begin(); itr != mTargetStorage->end(); ++itr)
60 delete itr->second;
61
62 delete mTargetStorage;
63 mCounterList.clear();
64}
65
66void SmartScript::OnReset()
67{
68 SetPhase(0);
69 ResetBaseObject();
70 for (SmartAIEventList::iterator i = mEvents.begin(); i != mEvents.end(); ++i)
71 {
72 if (!((*i).event.event_flags & SMART_EVENT_FLAG_DONT_RESET))
73 {
74 InitTimer((*i));
75 (*i).runOnce = false;
76 }
77 }
78 ProcessEventsFor(SMART_EVENT_RESET);
79 mLastInvoker.Clear();
80 mCounterList.clear();
81}
82
83void SmartScript::ProcessEventsFor(SMART_EVENT e, Unit* unit, uint32 var0, uint32 var1, bool bvar, const SpellInfo* spell, GameObject* gob)
84{
85 for (SmartAIEventList::iterator i = mEvents.begin(); i != mEvents.end(); ++i)
86 {
87 SMART_EVENT eventType = SMART_EVENT(i->GetEventType());
88 if (eventType == SMART_EVENT_LINK)//special handling
89 continue;
90
91 if (eventType == e /*&& (!i->event.event_phase_mask || IsInPhase(i->event.event_phase_mask)) && !(i->event.event_flags & SMART_EVENT_FLAG_NOT_REPEATABLE && i->runOnce)*/)
92 if (sConditionMgr->IsObjectMeetingSmartEventConditions(i->entryOrGuid, i->event_id, i->source_type, unit, GetBaseObject()))
93 ProcessEvent(*i, unit, var0, var1, bvar, spell, gob);
94 }
95}
96
97void SmartScript::ProcessAction(SmartScriptHolder& e, Unit* unit, uint32 var0, uint32 var1, bool bvar, const SpellInfo* spell, GameObject* gob)
98{
99 //calc random
100 if (e.GetEventType() != SMART_EVENT_LINK && e.event.event_chance < 100 && e.event.event_chance)
101 {
102 uint32 rnd = urand(0, 100);
103 if (e.event.event_chance <= rnd)
104 return;
105 }
106 e.runOnce = true;//used for repeat check
107
108 if (unit)
109 mLastInvoker = unit->GetGUID();
110
111 if (Unit* tempInvoker = GetLastInvoker())
112 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction: Invoker: %s (%s)", tempInvoker->GetName().c_str(), tempInvoker->GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
113
114 switch (e.GetActionType())
115 {
116 case SMART_ACTION_TALK:
117 {
118 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
119 Creature* talker = me;
120 Player* targetPlayer = NULL;
121 Unit* talkTarget = NULL;
122
123 if (targets)
124 {
125 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
126 {
127 if (IsCreature(*itr) && !(*itr)->ToCreature()->IsPet()) // Prevented sending text to pets.
128 {
129 if (e.action.talk.useTalkTarget)
130 talkTarget = (*itr)->ToCreature();
131 else
132 talker = (*itr)->ToCreature();
133 break;
134 }
135 else if (IsPlayer(*itr))
136 {
137 targetPlayer = (*itr)->ToPlayer();
138 break;
139 }
140 }
141
142 delete targets;
143 }
144
145 if (!talker)
146 break;
147
148 mTalkerEntry = talker->GetEntry();
149 mLastTextID = e.action.talk.textGroupID;
150 mTextTimer = e.action.talk.duration;
151
152 if (IsPlayer(GetLastInvoker())) // used for $vars in texts and whisper target
153 talkTarget = GetLastInvoker();
154 else if (targetPlayer)
155 talkTarget = targetPlayer;
156
157 mUseTextTimer = true;
158 sCreatureTextMgr->SendChat(talker, uint8(e.action.talk.textGroupID), talkTarget);
159 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction: SMART_ACTION_TALK: talker: %s (%s), textGuid: %s",
160 talker->GetName().c_str(), talker->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), talkTarget ? talkTarget->GetGUID().ToString().c_str() : "Empty");
161 break;
162 }
163 case SMART_ACTION_SIMPLE_TALK:
164 {
165 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
166 if (targets)
167 {
168 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
169 {
170 if (IsCreature(*itr))
171 sCreatureTextMgr->SendChat((*itr)->ToCreature(), uint8(e.action.talk.textGroupID), IsPlayer(GetLastInvoker()) ? GetLastInvoker() : 0);
172 else if (IsPlayer(*itr) && me)
173 {
174 Unit* templastInvoker = GetLastInvoker();
175 sCreatureTextMgr->SendChat(me, uint8(e.action.talk.textGroupID), IsPlayer(templastInvoker) ? templastInvoker : 0, CHAT_MSG_ADDON, LANG_ADDON, TEXT_RANGE_NORMAL, 0, TEAM_OTHER, false, (*itr)->ToPlayer());
176 }
177 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_SIMPLE_TALK: talker: %s (%s), textGroupId: %u",
178 (*itr)->GetName().c_str(), (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), uint8(e.action.talk.textGroupID));
179 }
180
181 delete targets;
182 }
183 break;
184 }
185 case SMART_ACTION_PLAY_EMOTE:
186 {
187 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
188 if (targets)
189 {
190 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
191 {
192 if (IsUnit(*itr))
193 {
194 (*itr)->ToUnit()->HandleEmoteCommand(e.action.emote.emote);
195 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_PLAY_EMOTE: target: %s (%s), emote: %u",
196 (*itr)->GetName().c_str(), (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.emote.emote);
197 }
198 }
199
200 delete targets;
201 }
202 break;
203 }
204 case SMART_ACTION_SOUND:
205 {
206 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
207 if (targets)
208 {
209 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
210 {
211 if (IsUnit(*itr))
212 {
213 (*itr)->PlayDirectSound(e.action.sound.sound, e.action.sound.onlySelf ? (*itr)->ToPlayer() : nullptr);
214 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_SOUND: target: %s (%s), sound: %u, onlyself: %u",
215 (*itr)->GetName().c_str(), (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.sound.sound, e.action.sound.onlySelf);
216 }
217 }
218
219 delete targets;
220 }
221 break;
222 }
223 case SMART_ACTION_SET_FACTION:
224 {
225 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
226 if (targets)
227 {
228 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
229 {
230 if (IsCreature(*itr))
231 {
232 if (e.action.faction.factionID)
233 {
234 (*itr)->ToCreature()->setFaction(e.action.faction.factionID);
235 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_SET_FACTION: Creature entry %u, %s set faction to %u",
236 (*itr)->GetEntry(), (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.faction.factionID);
237 }
238 else
239 {
240 if (CreatureTemplate const* ci = sObjectMgr->GetCreatureTemplate((*itr)->ToCreature()->GetEntry()))
241 {
242 if ((*itr)->ToCreature()->getFaction() != ci->faction)
243 {
244 (*itr)->ToCreature()->setFaction(ci->faction);
245 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_SET_FACTION: Creature entry %u, %s set faction to %u",
246 (*itr)->GetEntry(), (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), ci->faction);
247 }
248 }
249 }
250 }
251 }
252
253 delete targets;
254 }
255 break;
256 }
257 case SMART_ACTION_MORPH_TO_ENTRY_OR_MODEL:
258 {
259 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
260 if (!targets)
261 break;
262
263 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
264 {
265 if (!IsCreature(*itr))
266 continue;
267
268 if (e.action.morphOrMount.creature || e.action.morphOrMount.model)
269 {
270 //set model based on entry from creature_template
271 if (e.action.morphOrMount.creature)
272 {
273 if (CreatureTemplate const* ci = sObjectMgr->GetCreatureTemplate(e.action.morphOrMount.creature))
274 {
275 uint32 displayId = ObjectMgr::ChooseDisplayId(ci);
276 (*itr)->ToCreature()->SetDisplayId(displayId);
277 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_MORPH_TO_ENTRY_OR_MODEL: Creature entry %u, %s set displayid to %u",
278 (*itr)->GetEntry(), (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), displayId);
279 }
280 }
281 //if no param1, then use value from param2 (modelId)
282 else
283 {
284 (*itr)->ToCreature()->SetDisplayId(e.action.morphOrMount.model);
285 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_MORPH_TO_ENTRY_OR_MODEL: Creature entry %u, %s set displayid to %u",
286 (*itr)->GetEntry(), (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.morphOrMount.model);
287 }
288 }
289 else
290 {
291 (*itr)->ToCreature()->DeMorph();
292 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_MORPH_TO_ENTRY_OR_MODEL: Creature entry %u, %s demorphs.",
293 (*itr)->GetEntry(), (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
294 }
295 }
296
297 delete targets;
298 break;
299 }
300 case SMART_ACTION_FAIL_QUEST:
301 {
302 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
303 if (!targets)
304 break;
305
306 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
307 {
308 if (IsPlayer(*itr))
309 {
310 (*itr)->ToPlayer()->FailQuest(e.action.quest.quest);
311 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_FAIL_QUEST: Player %s fails quest %u",
312 (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.quest.quest);
313 }
314 }
315
316 delete targets;
317 break;
318 }
319 case SMART_ACTION_ADD_QUEST:
320 {
321 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
322 if (!targets)
323 break;
324
325 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
326 {
327 if (IsPlayer(*itr))
328 {
329 if (Quest const* q = sObjectMgr->GetQuestTemplate(e.action.quest.quest))
330 {
331 (*itr)->ToPlayer()->AddQuestAndCheckCompletion(q, NULL);
332 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_ADD_QUEST: Player %s add quest %u",
333 (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.quest.quest);
334 }
335 }
336 }
337
338 delete targets;
339 break;
340 }
341 case SMART_ACTION_SET_REACT_STATE:
342 {
343 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
344 if (!targets)
345 break;
346
347 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
348 {
349 if (!IsCreature(*itr))
350 continue;
351
352 (*itr)->ToCreature()->SetReactState(ReactStates(e.action.react.state));
353 }
354
355 delete targets;
356 break;
357 }
358 case SMART_ACTION_RANDOM_EMOTE:
359 {
360 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
361 if (!targets)
362 break;
363
364 uint32 emotes[SMART_ACTION_PARAM_COUNT];
365 emotes[0] = e.action.randomEmote.emote1;
366 emotes[1] = e.action.randomEmote.emote2;
367 emotes[2] = e.action.randomEmote.emote3;
368 emotes[3] = e.action.randomEmote.emote4;
369 emotes[4] = e.action.randomEmote.emote5;
370 emotes[5] = e.action.randomEmote.emote6;
371 uint32 temp[SMART_ACTION_PARAM_COUNT];
372 uint32 count = 0;
373 for (uint8 i = 0; i < SMART_ACTION_PARAM_COUNT; i++)
374 {
375 if (emotes[i])
376 {
377 temp[count] = emotes[i];
378 ++count;
379 }
380 }
381
382 if (count == 0)
383 {
384 delete targets;
385 break;
386 }
387
388 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
389 {
390 if (IsUnit(*itr))
391 {
392 uint32 emote = temp[urand(0, count - 1)];
393 (*itr)->ToUnit()->HandleEmoteCommand(emote);
394 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_RANDOM_EMOTE: Creature %s handle random emote %u",
395 (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), emote);
396 }
397 }
398
399 delete targets;
400 break;
401 }
402 case SMART_ACTION_THREAT_ALL_PCT:
403 {
404 if (!me)
405 break;
406
407 ThreatContainer::StorageType threatList = me->getThreatManager().getThreatList();
408 for (ThreatContainer::StorageType::const_iterator i = threatList.begin(); i != threatList.end(); ++i)
409 {
410 if (Unit* target = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(*me, (*i)->getUnitGuid()))
411 {
412 me->getThreatManager().modifyThreatPercent(target, e.action.threatPCT.threatINC ? (int32)e.action.threatPCT.threatINC : -(int32)e.action.threatPCT.threatDEC);
413 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_THREAT_ALL_PCT: Creature %s modify threat for %s, value %i",
414 me->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), target->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(),
415 e.action.threatPCT.threatINC ? (int32)e.action.threatPCT.threatINC : -(int32)e.action.threatPCT.threatDEC);
416 }
417 }
418 break;
419 }
420 case SMART_ACTION_THREAT_SINGLE_PCT:
421 {
422 if (!me)
423 break;
424
425 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
426 if (!targets)
427 break;
428
429 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
430 {
431 if (IsUnit(*itr))
432 {
433 me->getThreatManager().modifyThreatPercent((*itr)->ToUnit(), e.action.threatPCT.threatINC ? (int32)e.action.threatPCT.threatINC : -(int32)e.action.threatPCT.threatDEC);
434 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_THREAT_SINGLE_PCT: Creature %s modify threat for %s, value %i",
435 me->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(),
436 e.action.threatPCT.threatINC ? (int32)e.action.threatPCT.threatINC : -(int32)e.action.threatPCT.threatDEC);
437 }
438 }
439
440 delete targets;
441 break;
442 }
443 case SMART_ACTION_CALL_AREAEXPLOREDOREVENTHAPPENS:
444 {
445 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
446 if (!targets)
447 break;
448
449 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
450 {
451 // Special handling for vehicles
452 if (IsUnit(*itr))
453 if (Vehicle* vehicle = (*itr)->ToUnit()->GetVehicleKit())
454 for (SeatMap::iterator it = vehicle->Seats.begin(); it != vehicle->Seats.end(); ++it)
455 if (Player* player = ObjectAccessor::FindPlayer(it->second.Passenger.Guid))
456 player->AreaExploredOrEventHappens(e.action.quest.quest);
457
458 if (IsPlayer(*itr))
459 {
460 (*itr)->ToPlayer()->GroupEventHappens(e.action.quest.quest, me);
461
462 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_CALL_AREAEXPLOREDOREVENTHAPPENS: %s credited quest %u",
463 (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.quest.quest);
464 }
465 }
466
467 delete targets;
468 break;
469 }
470 case SMART_ACTION_CAST:
471 {
472 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
473 if (!targets)
474 break;
475
476 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
477 {
478 if (!IsUnit(*itr))
479 continue;
480
481 if (!(e.action.cast.flags & SMARTCAST_AURA_NOT_PRESENT) || !(*itr)->ToUnit()->HasAura(e.action.cast.spell))
482 {
483 if (me)
484 {
485 if (e.action.cast.flags & SMARTCAST_INTERRUPT_PREVIOUS)
486 me->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(false);
487
488 if (e.action.cast.flags & SMARTCAST_COMBAT_MOVE)
489 {
490 // If cast flag SMARTCAST_COMBAT_MOVE is set combat movement will not be allowed
491 // unless target is outside spell range, out of mana, or LOS.
492
493 bool _allowMove = false;
494 SpellInfo const* spellInfo = sSpellMgr->AssertSpellInfo(e.action.cast.spell);
495 std::vector<SpellInfo::CostData> costs = spellInfo->CalcPowerCost(me, spellInfo->GetSchoolMask());
496 bool hasPower = true;
497 for (SpellInfo::CostData const& cost : costs)
498 {
499 if (cost.Power == POWER_HEALTH)
500 {
501 if (me->GetHealth() <= uint32(cost.Amount))
502 {
503 hasPower = false;
504 break;
505 }
506 }
507 else
508 {
509 if (me->GetPower(cost.Power) < cost.Amount)
510 {
511 hasPower = false;
512 break;
513 }
514 }
515
516 }
517
518 if (me->GetDistance(*itr) > spellInfo->GetMaxRange(true) ||
519 me->GetDistance(*itr) < spellInfo->GetMinRange(true) ||
520 !me->IsWithinLOSInMap(*itr) || !hasPower)
521 _allowMove = true;
522
523 ENSURE_AI(SmartAI, me->AI())->SetCombatMove(_allowMove);
524 }
525
526 me->CastSpell((*itr)->ToUnit(), e.action.cast.spell, (e.action.cast.flags & SMARTCAST_TRIGGERED) != 0);
527 }
528 else if (go)
529 go->CastSpell((*itr)->ToUnit(), e.action.cast.spell, (e.action.cast.flags & SMARTCAST_TRIGGERED) != 0);
530
531 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_CAST:: %s casts spell %u on target %s with castflags %u",
532 (me ? me->GetGUID() : go->GetGUID()).ToString().c_str(), e.action.cast.spell, (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.cast.flags);
533 }
534 else
535 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "Spell %u not cast because it has flag SMARTCAST_AURA_NOT_PRESENT and the target (%s) already has the aura", e.action.cast.spell, (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
536 }
537
538 delete targets;
539 break;
540 }
541 case SMART_ACTION_INVOKER_CAST:
542 {
543 Unit* tempLastInvoker = GetLastInvoker();
544 if (!tempLastInvoker)
545 break;
546
547 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
548 if (!targets)
549 break;
550
551 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
552 {
553 if (!IsUnit(*itr))
554 continue;
555
556 if (!(e.action.cast.flags & SMARTCAST_AURA_NOT_PRESENT) || !(*itr)->ToUnit()->HasAura(e.action.cast.spell))
557 {
558 if (e.action.cast.flags & SMARTCAST_INTERRUPT_PREVIOUS)
559 tempLastInvoker->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(false);
560
561 tempLastInvoker->CastSpell((*itr)->ToUnit(), e.action.cast.spell, (e.action.cast.flags & SMARTCAST_TRIGGERED) != 0);
562 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_INVOKER_CAST: Invoker %s casts spell %u on target %s with castflags %u",
563 tempLastInvoker->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.cast.spell, (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), e.action.cast.flags);
564 }
565 else
566 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "Spell %u not cast because it has flag SMARTCAST_AURA_NOT_PRESENT and the target (%s) already has the aura", e.action.cast.spell, (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
567 }
568
569 delete targets;
570 break;
571 }
572 case SMART_ACTION_ADD_AURA:
573 {
574 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
575 if (!targets)
576 break;
577
578 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
579 {
580 if (IsUnit(*itr))
581 {
582 (*itr)->ToUnit()->AddAura(e.action.cast.spell, (*itr)->ToUnit());
583 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_ADD_AURA: Adding aura %u to %s",
584 e.action.cast.spell, (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
585 }
586 }
587
588 delete targets;
589 break;
590 }
591 case SMART_ACTION_ACTIVATE_GOBJECT:
592 {
593 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
594 if (!targets)
595 break;
596
597 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
598 {
599 if (IsGameObject(*itr))
600 {
601 // Activate
602 (*itr)->ToGameObject()->SetLootState(GO_READY);
603 (*itr)->ToGameObject()->UseDoorOrButton(0, false, unit);
604 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_ACTIVATE_GOBJECT. %s (entry: %u) activated",
605 (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), (*itr)->GetEntry());
606 }
607 }
608
609 delete targets;
610 break;
611 }
612 case SMART_ACTION_RESET_GOBJECT:
613 {
614 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
615 if (!targets)
616 break;
617
618 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
619 {
620 if (IsGameObject(*itr))
621 {
622 (*itr)->ToGameObject()->ResetDoorOrButton();
623 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::ProcessAction:: SMART_ACTION_RESET_GOBJECT. %s (entry: %u) reset",
624 (*itr)->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), (*itr)->GetEntry());
625 }
626 }
627
628 delete targets;
629 break;
630 }
631 case SMART_ACTION_SET_EMOTE_STATE:
632 {
633 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
634 if (!targets)
635 break;
636
637 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)
638 {
639 if (IsUnit(*itr))
640 {
641 (*itr)->ToUnit()->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_NPC_EMOTESTATE, e.action.emote.emote);

2277 break;

2282 case SMART_ACTION_START_CLOSEST_WAYPOINT:
2283 {
2284 uint32 waypoints[SMART_ACTION_PARAM_COUNT];
2285 waypoints[0] = e.action.closestWaypointFromList.wp1;
2286 waypoints[1] = e.action.closestWaypointFromList.wp2;
2287 waypoints[2] = e.action.closestWaypointFromList.wp3;
2288 waypoints[3] = e.action.closestWaypointFromList.wp4;
2289 waypoints[4] = e.action.closestWaypointFromList.wp5;
2290 waypoints[5] = e.action.closestWaypointFromList.wp6;
2291 float distanceToClosest = std::numeric_limits<float>::max();
2292 WayPoint* closestWp = NULL;
2293
2294 ObjectList* targets = GetTargets(e, unit);
2295 if (targets)
2296 {
2297 for (ObjectList::iterator itr = targets->begin(); itr != targets->end(); ++itr)

2299 if (Creature* target = (*itr)->ToCreature())
2300 {
2301 if (IsSmart(target))
2302 {
2303 for (uint8 i = 0; i < SMART_ACTION_PARAM_COUNT; i++)
2304 {
2305 if (!waypoints[i])
2306 continue;
2307
2308 WPPath* path = sSmartWaypointMgr->GetPath(waypoints[i]);
2309
2310 if (!path || path->empty())
2311 continue;
2312
2313 WPPath::const_iterator itrWp = path->find(0);
2314
2315 if (itrWp != path->end())
2316 {
2317 if (WayPoint* wp = itrWp->second)
2318 {
2319 float distToThisPath = target->GetDistance(wp->x, wp->y, wp->z);
2320
2321 if (distToThisPath < distanceToClosest)
2322 {
2323 distanceToClosest = distToThisPath;
2324 closestWp = wp;
2325 }
2326 }
2327 }
2328 }
2329
2330 if (closestWp)
2331 CAST_AI(SmartAI, target->AI())->StartPath(false, closestWp->id, true);
2332 }
2333 }
2334 }
2335
2336 delete targets;
2337 }
2338 break;
2339 }
2340 default:
2341 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "SmartScript::ProcessAction: Entry " SI64FMTD " SourceType %u, Event %u, Unhandled Action type %u", e.entryOrGuid, e.GetScriptType(), e.event_id, e.GetActionType());
2342 break;
2343 }
2344
2345 if (e.link && e.link != e.event_id)
2346 {
2347 SmartScriptHolder& linked = SmartAIMgr::FindLinkedEvent(mEvents, e.link);
2348 if (linked)
2349 ProcessEvent(linked, unit, var0, var1, bvar, spell, gob);
2350 else
2351 TC_LOG_DEBUG("sql.sql", "SmartScript::ProcessAction: Entry " SI64FMTD " SourceType %u, Event %u, Link Event %u not found or invalid, skipped.", e.entryOrGuid, e.GetScriptType(), e.event_id, e.link);
2352 }

2440}

2447 script.event.raw.param2 = event_param2;

2449 script.event.raw.param4 = event_param4;
2450 script.event.event_phase_mask = phaseMask;
2451 script.event.event_flags = event_flags;
2452 script.event.event_chance = 100;
2453
2454 script.action.type = action;
2455 script.action.raw.param1 = action_param1;
2456 script.action.raw.param2 = action_param2;
2457 script.action.raw.param3 = action_param3;
2458 script.action.raw.param4 = action_param4;
2459 script.action.raw.param5 = action_param5;
2460 script.action.raw.param6 = action_param6;
2461
2462 script.target.type = t;
2463 script.target.raw.param1 = target_param1;

2465 script.target.raw.param3 = target_param3;

2471
2472ObjectList* SmartScript::GetTargets(SmartScriptHolder const& e, Unit* invoker /*= NULL*/)
2473{
2474 Unit* scriptTrigger = NULL;
2475 if (invoker)
2476 scriptTrigger = invoker;
2477 else if (Unit* tempLastInvoker = GetLastInvoker())
2478 scriptTrigger = tempLastInvoker;
2479
2480 WorldObject* baseObject = GetBaseObject();
2481
2482 ObjectList* l = new ObjectList();
2483 switch (e.GetTargetType())
2484 {
2485 case SMART_TARGET_SELF:
2486 if (baseObject)
2487 l->push_back(baseObject);
2488 break;
2489 case SMART_TARGET_VICTIM:
2490 if (me)
2491 if (Unit* victim = me->GetVictim())
2492 l->push_back(victim);
2493 break;
2494 case SMART_TARGET_HOSTILE_SECOND_AGGRO:
2495 if (me)
2496 if (Unit* u = me->AI()->SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_TOPAGGRO, 1))
2497 l->push_back(u);
2498 break;
2499 case SMART_TARGET_HOSTILE_LAST_AGGRO:
2500 if (me)
2501 if (Unit* u = me->AI()->SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_BOTTOMAGGRO, 0))
2502 l->push_back(u);
2503 break;
2504 case SMART_TARGET_HOSTILE_RANDOM:
2505 if (me)
2506 if (Unit* u = me->AI()->SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 0))
2507 l->push_back(u);
2508 break;
2509 case SMART_TARGET_HOSTILE_RANDOM_NOT_TOP:
2510 if (me)
2511 if (Unit* u = me->AI()->SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 1))
2512 l->push_back(u);
2513 break;
2514 case SMART_TARGET_ACTION_INVOKER:
2515 if (scriptTrigger)
2516 l->push_back(scriptTrigger);
2517 break;
2518 case SMART_TARGET_ACTION_INVOKER_VEHICLE:
2519 if (scriptTrigger && scriptTrigger->GetVehicle() && scriptTrigger->GetVehicle()->GetBase())
2520 l->push_back(scriptTrigger->GetVehicle()->GetBase());
2521 break;
2522 case SMART_TARGET_INVOKER_PARTY:
2523 if (scriptTrigger)
2524 {
2525 if (Player* player = scriptTrigger->ToPlayer())
2526 {
2527 if (Group* group = player->GetGroup())
2528 {
2529 for (GroupReference* groupRef = group->GetFirstMember(); groupRef != NULL; groupRef = groupRef->next())
2530 if (Player* member = groupRef->GetSource())
2531 l->push_back(member);
2532 }
2533 // We still add the player to the list if there is no group. If we do
2534 // this even if there is a group (thus the else-check), it will add the
2535 // same player to the list twice. We don't want that to happen.
2536 else
2537 l->push_back(scriptTrigger);
2538 }
2539 }
2540 break;
2541 case SMART_TARGET_CREATURE_RANGE:
2542 {
2543 // will always return a valid pointer, even if empty list
2544 ObjectList* units = GetWorldObjectsInDist((float)e.target.unitRange.maxDist);
2545 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = units->begin(); itr != units->end(); ++itr)
2546 {
2547 if (!IsCreature(*itr))
2548 continue;
2549
2550 if (me && me->GetGUID() == (*itr)->GetGUID())
2551 continue;
2552
2553 if ((!e.target.unitRange.creature || (*itr)->ToCreature()->GetEntry() == e.target.unitRange.creature) && baseObject->IsInRange(*itr, float(e.target.unitRange.minDist), float(e.target.unitRange.maxDist)))
2554 l->push_back(*itr);
2555 }
2556
2557 delete units;
2558 break;
2559 }
2560 case SMART_TARGET_CREATURE_DISTANCE:
2561 {
2562 // will always return a valid pointer, even if empty list
2563 ObjectList* units = GetWorldObjectsInDist((float)e.target.unitDistance.dist);
2564 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = units->begin(); itr != units->end(); ++itr)
2565 {
2566 if (!IsCreature(*itr))
2567 continue;
2568
2569 if (me && me->GetGUID() == (*itr)->GetGUID())
2570 continue;
2571
2572 if (!e.target.unitDistance.creature || (*itr)->ToCreature()->GetEntry() == e.target.unitDistance.creature)
2573 l->push_back(*itr);
2574 }
2575
2576 delete units;
2577 break;
2578 }
2579 case SMART_TARGET_GAMEOBJECT_DISTANCE:
2580 {
2581 // will always return a valid pointer, even if empty list
2582 ObjectList* units = GetWorldObjectsInDist((float)e.target.goDistance.dist);
2583 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = units->begin(); itr != units->end(); ++itr)
2584 {
2585 if (!IsGameObject(*itr))
2586 continue;
2587
2588 if (go && go->GetGUID() == (*itr)->GetGUID())
2589 continue;
2590
2591 if (!e.target.goDistance.entry || (*itr)->ToGameObject()->GetEntry() == e.target.goDistance.entry)
2592 l->push_back(*itr);
2593 }
2594
2595 delete units;
2596 break;
2597 }
2598 case SMART_TARGET_GAMEOBJECT_RANGE:
2599 {
2600 // will always return a valid pointer, even if empty list
2601 ObjectList* units = GetWorldObjectsInDist((float)e.target.goRange.maxDist);
2602 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = units->begin(); itr != units->end(); ++itr)
2603 {
2604 if (!IsGameObject(*itr))
2605 continue;
2606
2607 if (go && go->GetGUID() == (*itr)->GetGUID())
2608 continue;
2609
2610 if ((!e.target.goRange.entry && (*itr)->ToGameObject()->GetEntry() == e.target.goRange.entry) && baseObject->IsInRange(*itr, float(e.target.goRange.minDist), float(e.target.goRange.maxDist)))
2611 l->push_back(*itr);
2612 }
2613
2614 delete units;
2615 break;
2616 }
2617 case SMART_TARGET_CREATURE_GUID:
2618 {
2619 if (!scriptTrigger && !baseObject)
2620 {
2621 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "SMART_TARGET_CREATURE_GUID can not be used without invoker");
2622 break;
2623 }
2624
2625 if (Creature* target = FindCreatureNear(scriptTrigger ? scriptTrigger : baseObject, e.target.unitGUID.dbGuid))
2626 if (!e.target.unitGUID.entry || target->GetEntry() == e.target.unitGUID.entry)
2627 l->push_back(target);
2628 break;
2629 }
2630 case SMART_TARGET_GAMEOBJECT_GUID:
2631 {
2632 if (!scriptTrigger && !baseObject)
2633 {
2634 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "SMART_TARGET_GAMEOBJECT_GUID can not be used without invoker");
2635 break;
2636 }
2637
2638 if (GameObject* target = FindGameObjectNear(scriptTrigger ? scriptTrigger : baseObject, e.target.goGUID.dbGuid))
2639 if (!e.target.goGUID.entry || target->GetEntry() == e.target.goGUID.entry)
2640 l->push_back(target);
2641 break;
2642 }
2643 case SMART_TARGET_PLAYER_RANGE:
2644 {
2645 // will always return a valid pointer, even if empty list
2646 ObjectList* units = GetWorldObjectsInDist((float)e.target.playerRange.maxDist);
2647 if (!units->empty() && baseObject)
2648 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = units->begin(); itr != units->end(); ++itr)
2649 if (IsPlayer(*itr) && baseObject->IsInRange(*itr, (float)e.target.playerRange.minDist, (float)e.target.playerRange.maxDist))
2650 l->push_back(*itr);
2651
2652 delete units;
2653 break;
2654 }
2655 case SMART_TARGET_PLAYER_DISTANCE:
2656 {
2657 // will always return a valid pointer, even if empty list
2658 ObjectList* units = GetWorldObjectsInDist((float)e.target.playerDistance.dist);
2659 for (ObjectList::const_iterator itr = units->begin(); itr != units->end(); ++itr)
2660 if (IsPlayer(*itr))
2661 l->push_back(*itr);
2662
2663 delete units;
2664 break;
2665 }
2666 case SMART_TARGET_STORED:
2667 {
2668 ObjectListMap::iterator itr = mTargetStorage->find(e.target.stored.id);
2669 if (itr != mTargetStorage->end())
2670 {
2671 ObjectList* objectList = itr->second->GetObjectList();
2672 l->assign(objectList->begin(), objectList->end());
2673 }
2674
2675 return l;
2676 }
2677 case SMART_TARGET_CLOSEST_CREATURE:
2678 {
2679 if (Creature* target = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(baseObject, e.target.closest.entry, float(e.target.closest.dist ? e.target.closest.dist : 100), !e.target.closest.dead))
2680 l->push_back(target);
2681 break;
2682 }
2683 case SMART_TARGET_CLOSEST_GAMEOBJECT:
2684 {
2685 if (GameObject* target = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(baseObject, e.target.closest.entry, float(e.target.closest.dist ? e.target.closest.dist : 100)))
2686 l->push_back(target);
2687 break;
2688 }
2689 case SMART_TARGET_CLOSEST_PLAYER:
2690 {
2691 if (me)
2692 if (Player* target = me->SelectNearestPlayer(float(e.target.playerDistance.dist)))
2693 l->push_back(target);
2694 break;
2695 }
2696 case SMART_TARGET_OWNER_OR_SUMMONER:
2697 {
2698 if (me)
2699 {
2700 ObjectGuid charmerOrOwnerGuid = me->GetCharmerOrOwnerGUID();
2701
2702 if (!charmerOrOwnerGuid)
2703 charmerOrOwnerGuid = me->GetCreatorGUID();
2704
2705 if (Unit* owner = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(*me, charmerOrOwnerGuid))
2706 l->push_back(owner);
2707 }
2708 break;
2709 }
2710 case SMART_TARGET_THREAT_LIST:
2711 {
2712 if (me)
2713 {
2714 ThreatContainer::StorageType threatList = me->getThreatManager().getThreatList();
2715 for (ThreatContainer::StorageType::const_iterator i = threatList.begin(); i != threatList.end(); ++i)
2716 if (Unit* temp = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(*me, (*i)->getUnitGuid()))
2717 l->push_back(temp);
2718 }
2719 break;
2720 }
2721 case SMART_TARGET_CLOSEST_ENEMY:
2722 {
2723 if (me)
2724 if (Unit* target = me->SelectNearestTarget(e.target.closestAttackable.maxDist, e.target.closestAttackable.playerOnly != 0))
2725 l->push_back(target);
2726 break;
2727 }
2728 case SMART_TARGET_CLOSEST_FRIENDLY:
2729 {
2730 if (me)
2731 if (Unit* target = DoFindClosestFriendlyInRange(e.target.closestFriendly.maxDist, e.target.closestFriendly.playerOnly != 0))
2732 l->push_back(target);
2733 break;
2734 }
2735 case SMART_TARGET_POSITION:
2736 case SMART_TARGET_NONE:
2737 default:
2738 break;
2739 }
2740
2741 if (l->empty())
2742 {
2743 delete l;
2744 l = NULL;
2745 }
2746
2747 return l;
2748}
2749
2750ObjectList* SmartScript::GetWorldObjectsInDist(float dist)
2751{
2752 ObjectList* targets = new ObjectList();
2753 WorldObject* obj = GetBaseObject();
2754 if (obj)
2755 {
2756 Trinity::AllWorldObjectsInRange u_check(obj, dist);
2757 Trinity::WorldObjectListSearcher<Trinity::AllWorldObjectsInRange> searcher(obj, *targets, u_check);
2758 obj->VisitNearbyObject(dist, searcher);
2759 }
2760 return targets;
2761}
2762
2763void SmartScript::ProcessEvent(SmartScriptHolder& e, Unit* unit, uint32 var0, uint32 var1, bool bvar, const SpellInfo* spell, GameObject* gob)
2764{
2765 if (!e.active && e.GetEventType() != SMART_EVENT_LINK)
2766 return;
2767
2768 if ((e.event.event_phase_mask && !IsInPhase(e.event.event_phase_mask)) || ((e.event.event_flags & SMART_EVENT_FLAG_NOT_REPEATABLE) && e.runOnce))
2769 return;
2770
2771 switch (e.GetEventType())
2772 {
2773 case SMART_EVENT_LINK://special handling
2774 ProcessAction(e, unit, var0, var1, bvar, spell, gob);
2775 break;
2776 //called from Update tick
2777 case SMART_EVENT_UPDATE:
2778 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMin, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMax);
2779 break;
2780 case SMART_EVENT_UPDATE_OOC:
2781 if (me && me->IsInCombat())
2782 return;
2783 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMin, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMax);
2784 break;
2785 case SMART_EVENT_UPDATE_IC:
2786 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat())
2787 return;
2788 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMin, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMax);
2789 break;
2790 case SMART_EVENT_HEALT_PCT:
2791 {
2792 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat() || !me->GetMaxHealth())
2793 return;
2794 uint32 perc = (uint32)me->GetHealthPct();
2795 if (perc > e.event.minMaxRepeat.max || perc < e.event.minMaxRepeat.min)
2796 return;
2797 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMin, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMax);
2798 break;
2799 }
2800 case SMART_EVENT_TARGET_HEALTH_PCT:
2801 {
2802 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat() || !me->GetVictim() || !me->EnsureVictim()->GetMaxHealth())
2803 return;
2804 uint32 perc = (uint32)me->EnsureVictim()->GetHealthPct();
2805 if (perc > e.event.minMaxRepeat.max || perc < e.event.minMaxRepeat.min)
2806 return;
2807 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMin, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMax, me->GetVictim());
2808 break;
2809 }
2810 case SMART_EVENT_MANA_PCT:
2811 {
2812 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat() || !me->GetMaxPower(POWER_MANA))
2813 return;
2814 uint32 perc = uint32(100.0f * me->GetPower(POWER_MANA) / me->GetMaxPower(POWER_MANA));
2815 if (perc > e.event.minMaxRepeat.max || perc < e.event.minMaxRepeat.min)
2816 return;
2817 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMin, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMax);
2818 break;
2819 }
2820 case SMART_EVENT_TARGET_MANA_PCT:
2821 {
2822 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat() || !me->GetVictim() || !me->EnsureVictim()->GetMaxPower(POWER_MANA))
2823 return;
2824 uint32 perc = uint32(100.0f * me->EnsureVictim()->GetPower(POWER_MANA) / me->EnsureVictim()->GetMaxPower(POWER_MANA));
2825 if (perc > e.event.minMaxRepeat.max || perc < e.event.minMaxRepeat.min)
2826 return;
2827 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMin, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMax, me->GetVictim());
2828 break;
2829 }
2830 case SMART_EVENT_RANGE:
2831 {
2832 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat() || !me->GetVictim())
2833 return;
2834
2835 if (me->IsInRange(me->GetVictim(), (float)e.event.minMaxRepeat.min, (float)e.event.minMaxRepeat.max))
2836 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMin, e.event.minMaxRepeat.repeatMax, me->GetVictim());
2837 break;
2838 }
2839 case SMART_EVENT_VICTIM_CASTING:
2840 {
2841 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat())
2842 return;
2843
2844 Unit* victim = me->GetVictim();
2845
2846 if (!victim || !victim->IsNonMeleeSpellCast(false, false, true))
2847 return;
2848
2849 if (e.event.targetCasting.spellId > 0)
2850 if (Spell* currSpell = victim->GetCurrentSpell(CURRENT_GENERIC_SPELL))
2851 if (currSpell->m_spellInfo->Id != e.event.targetCasting.spellId)
2852 return;
2853
2854 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.targetCasting.repeatMin, e.event.targetCasting.repeatMax, me->GetVictim());
2855 break;
2856 }
2857 case SMART_EVENT_FRIENDLY_HEALTH:
2858 {
2859 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat())
2860 return;
2861
2862 Unit* target = DoSelectLowestHpFriendly((float)e.event.friendlyHealth.radius, e.event.friendlyHealth.hpDeficit);
2863 if (!target || !target->IsInCombat())
2864 return;
2865 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.friendlyHealth.repeatMin, e.event.friendlyHealth.repeatMax, target);
2866 break;
2867 }
2868 case SMART_EVENT_FRIENDLY_IS_CC:
2869 {
2870 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat())
2871 return;
2872
2873 std::list<Creature*> pList;
2874 DoFindFriendlyCC(pList, (float)e.event.friendlyCC.radius);
2875 if (pList.empty())
2876 return;
2877 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.friendlyCC.repeatMin, e.event.friendlyCC.repeatMax, *pList.begin());
2878 break;
2879 }
2880 case SMART_EVENT_FRIENDLY_MISSING_BUFF:
2881 {
2882 std::list<Creature*> pList;
2883 DoFindFriendlyMissingBuff(pList, (float)e.event.missingBuff.radius, e.event.missingBuff.spell);
2884
2885 if (pList.empty())
2886 return;
2887
2888 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.missingBuff.repeatMin, e.event.missingBuff.repeatMax, *pList.begin());
2889 break;
2890 }
2891 case SMART_EVENT_HAS_AURA:
2892 {
2893 if (!me)
2894 return;
2895 uint32 count = me->GetAuraCount(e.event.aura.spell);
2896 if ((!e.event.aura.count && !count) || (e.event.aura.count && count >= e.event.aura.count))
2897 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.aura.repeatMin, e.event.aura.repeatMax);
2898 break;
2899 }
2900 case SMART_EVENT_TARGET_BUFFED:
2901 {
2902 if (!me || !me->GetVictim())
2903 return;
2904 uint32 count = me->EnsureVictim()->GetAuraCount(e.event.aura.spell);
2905 if (count < e.event.aura.count)
2906 return;
2907 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.aura.repeatMin, e.event.aura.repeatMax);
2908 break;
2909 }
2910 //no params
2911 case SMART_EVENT_AGGRO:
2912 case SMART_EVENT_DEATH:
2913 case SMART_EVENT_EVADE:
2914 case SMART_EVENT_REACHED_HOME:
2915 case SMART_EVENT_CHARMED:
2916 case SMART_EVENT_CHARMED_TARGET:
2917 case SMART_EVENT_CORPSE_REMOVED:
2918 case SMART_EVENT_AI_INIT:
2919 case SMART_EVENT_TRANSPORT_ADDPLAYER:
2920 case SMART_EVENT_TRANSPORT_REMOVE_PLAYER:
2921 case SMART_EVENT_QUEST_ACCEPTED:
2922 case SMART_EVENT_QUEST_OBJ_COPLETETION:
2923 case SMART_EVENT_QUEST_COMPLETION:
2924 case SMART_EVENT_QUEST_REWARDED:
2925 case SMART_EVENT_QUEST_FAIL:
2926 case SMART_EVENT_JUST_SUMMONED:
2927 case SMART_EVENT_RESET:
2928 case SMART_EVENT_JUST_CREATED:
2929 case SMART_EVENT_GOSSIP_HELLO:
2930 case SMART_EVENT_FOLLOW_COMPLETED:
2931 case SMART_EVENT_ON_SPELLCLICK:
2932 ProcessAction(e, unit, var0, var1, bvar, spell, gob);
2933 break;
2934 case SMART_EVENT_IS_BEHIND_TARGET:
2935 {
2936 if (!me)
2937 return;
2938
2939 if (Unit* victim = me->GetVictim())
2940 {
2941 if (!victim->HasInArc(static_cast<float>(M_PI), me))
2942 ProcessTimedAction(e, e.event.behindTarget.cooldownMin, e.event.behindTarget.cooldownMax, victim);
2943 }
2944 break;
2945 }
2946 case SMART_EVENT_RECEIVE_EMOTE:
2947 if (e.event.emote.emote == var0)
2948 {
2949 ProcessAction(e, unit);
2950 RecalcTimer(e, e.event.emote.cooldownMin, e.event.emote.cooldownMax);
2951 }
2952 break;
2953 case SMART_EVENT_KILL:
2954 {
2955 if (!me || !unit)
2956 return;
2957 if (e.event.kill.playerOnly && unit->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
2958 return;
2959 if (e.event.kill.creature && unit->GetEntry() != e.event.kill.creature)
2960 return;
2961 ProcessAction(e, unit);
2962 RecalcTimer(e, e.event.kill.cooldownMin, e.event.kill.cooldownMax);
2963 break;
2964 }
2965 case SMART_EVENT_SPELLHIT_TARGET:
2966 case SMART_EVENT_SPELLHIT:
2967 {
2968 if (!spell)
2969 return;
2970 if ((!e.event.spellHit.spell || spell->Id == e.event.spellHit.spell) &&
2971 (!e.event.spellHit.school || (spell->SchoolMask & e.event.spellHit.school)))
2972 {
2973 ProcessAction(e, unit, 0, 0, bvar, spell);
2974 RecalcTimer(e, e.event.spellHit.cooldownMin, e.event.spellHit.cooldownMax);
2975 }
2976 break;
2977 }
2978 case SMART_EVENT_OOC_LOS:
2979 {
2980 if (!me || me->IsInCombat())
2981 return;
2982 //can trigger if closer than fMaxAllowedRange
2983 float range = (float)e.event.los.maxDist;
2984
2985 //if range is ok and we are actually in LOS
2986 if (me->IsWithinDistInMap(unit, range) && me->IsWithinLOSInMap(unit))
2987 {
2988 //if friendly event&&who is not hostile OR hostile event&&who is hostile
2989 if ((e.event.los.noHostile && !me->IsHostileTo(unit)) ||
2990 (!e.event.los.noHostile && me->IsHostileTo(unit)))
2991 {
2992 ProcessAction(e, unit);
2993 RecalcTimer(e, e.event.los.cooldownMin, e.event.los.cooldownMax);
2994 }
2995 }
2996 break;
2997 }
2998 case SMART_EVENT_IC_LOS:
2999 {
3000 if (!me || !me->IsInCombat())
3001 return;
3002 //can trigger if closer than fMaxAllowedRange
3003 float range = (float)e.event.los.maxDist;
3004
3005 //if range is ok and we are actually in LOS

3327void SmartScript::UpdateTimer(SmartScriptHolder& e, uint32 const diff)
3328{
3329 if (e.GetEventType() == SMART_EVENT_LINK)
3330 return;
3331
3332 if (e.event.event_phase_mask && !IsInPhase(e.event.event_phase_mask))
3333 return;
3334
3335 if (e.GetEventType() == SMART_EVENT_UPDATE_IC && (!me || !me->IsInCombat()))
3336 return;
3337
3338 if (e.GetEventType() == SMART_EVENT_UPDATE_OOC && (me && me->IsInCombat())) //can be used with me=NULL (go script)
3339 return;
3340
3341 if (e.timer < diff)
3342 {
3343 // delay spell cast event if another spell is being cast
3344 if (e.GetActionType() == SMART_ACTION_CAST)
3345 {
3346 if (!(e.action.cast.flags & SMARTCAST_INTERRUPT_PREVIOUS))
3347 {
3348 if (me && me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
3349 {
3350 e.timer = 1;
3351 return;
3352 }
3353 }
3354 }
3355
3356 e.active = true;//activate events with cooldown
3357 switch (e.GetEventType())//process ONLY timed events
3358 {
3359 case SMART_EVENT_UPDATE:
3360 case SMART_EVENT_UPDATE_OOC:
3361 case SMART_EVENT_UPDATE_IC:
3362 case SMART_EVENT_HEALT_PCT:
3363 case SMART_EVENT_TARGET_HEALTH_PCT:
3364 case SMART_EVENT_MANA_PCT:
3365 case SMART_EVENT_TARGET_MANA_PCT:
3366 case SMART_EVENT_RANGE:
3367 case SMART_EVENT_VICTIM_CASTING:
3368 case SMART_EVENT_FRIENDLY_HEALTH:
3369 case SMART_EVENT_FRIENDLY_IS_CC:
3370 case SMART_EVENT_FRIENDLY_MISSING_BUFF:
3371 case SMART_EVENT_HAS_AURA:
3372 case SMART_EVENT_TARGET_BUFFED:
3373 case SMART_EVENT_IS_BEHIND_TARGET:
3374 case SMART_EVENT_FRIENDLY_HEALTH_PCT:
3375 case SMART_EVENT_DISTANCE_CREATURE:
3376 case SMART_EVENT_DISTANCE_GAMEOBJECT:
3377 {
3378 ProcessEvent(e);
3379 if (e.GetScriptType() == SMART_SCRIPT_TYPE_TIMED_ACTIONLIST)
3380 {
3381 e.enableTimed = false;//disable event if it is in an ActionList and was processed once
3382 for (SmartAIEventList::iterator i = mTimedActionList.begin(); i != mTimedActionList.end(); ++i)
3383 {
3384 //find the first event which is not the current one and enable it
3385 if (i->event_id > e.event_id)
3386 {
3387 i->enableTimed = true;
3388 break;
3389 }
3390 }
3391 }
3392 break;
3393 }
3394 }
3395 }
3396 else
3397 e.timer -= diff;
3398}

3416void SmartScript::OnUpdate(uint32 const diff)
3417{
3418 if ((mScriptType == SMART_SCRIPT_TYPE_CREATURE || mScriptType == SMART_SCRIPT_TYPE_GAMEOBJECT) && !GetBaseObject())
3419 return;
3420
3421 InstallEvents();//before UpdateTimers
3422
3423 for (SmartAIEventList::iterator i = mEvents.begin(); i != mEvents.end(); ++i)
3424 UpdateTimer(*i, diff);
3425
3426 if (!mStoredEvents.empty())
3427 for (SmartAIEventList::iterator i = mStoredEvents.begin(); i != mStoredEvents.end(); ++i)
3428 UpdateTimer(*i, diff);
3429
3430 bool needCleanup = true;
3431 if (!mTimedActionList.empty())
3432 {
3433 isProcessingTimedActionList = true;
3434 for (SmartAIEventList::iterator i = mTimedActionList.begin(); i != mTimedActionList.end(); ++i)
3435 {
3436 if ((*i).enableTimed)
3437 {
3438 UpdateTimer(*i, diff);
3439 needCleanup = false;
3440 }
3441 }
3442
3443 isProcessingTimedActionList = false;
3444 }
3445 if (needCleanup)
3446 mTimedActionList.clear();
3447
3448 if (!mRemIDs.empty())
3449 {
3450 for (std::list<uint32>::iterator i = mRemIDs.begin(); i != mRemIDs.end(); ++i)
3451 {
3452 RemoveStoredEvent((*i));
3453 }
3454 }
3455 if (mUseTextTimer && me)
3456 {
3457 if (mTextTimer < diff)
3458 {
3459 uint32 textID = mLastTextID;
3460 mLastTextID = 0;
3461 uint32 entry = mTalkerEntry;
3462 mTalkerEntry = 0;
3463 mTextTimer = 0;
3464 mUseTextTimer = false;
3465 ProcessEventsFor(SMART_EVENT_TEXT_OVER, NULL, textID, entry);
3466 } else mTextTimer -= diff;
3467 }
3468}

3470void SmartScript::FillScript(SmartAIEventList e, WorldObject* obj, AreaTriggerEntry const* at)
3471{
3472 if (e.empty())
3473 {
3474 if (obj)
3475 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript: EventMap for Entry %u is empty but is using SmartScript.", obj->GetEntry());
3476 if (at)
3477 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript: EventMap for AreaTrigger %u is empty but is using SmartScript.", at->ID);
3478 return;
3479 }
3480 for (SmartAIEventList::iterator i = e.begin(); i != e.end(); ++i)
3481 {
3482 #ifndef TRINITY_DEBUG
3483 if ((*i).event.event_flags & SMART_EVENT_FLAG_DEBUG_ONLY)
3484 continue;
3485 #endif
3486
3487 if ((*i).event.event_flags & SMART_EVENT_FLAG_DIFFICULTY_ALL)//if has instance flag add only if in it
3488 {
3489 if (obj && obj->GetMap()->IsDungeon())
3490 {
3491 if ((1 << (obj->GetMap()->GetSpawnMode()+1)) & (*i).event.event_flags)
3492 {
3493 mEvents.push_back((*i));
3494 }
3495 }
3496 continue;
3497 }
3498 mEvents.push_back((*i));//NOTE: 'world(0)' events still get processed in ANY instance mode
3499 }
3500 if (mEvents.empty() && obj)
3501 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "SmartScript: Entry %u has events but no events added to list because of instance flags.", obj->GetEntry());
3502 if (mEvents.empty() && at)
3503 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "SmartScript: AreaTrigger %u has events but no events added to list because of instance flags. NOTE: triggers can not handle any instance flags.", at->ID);
3504}

3530void SmartScript::OnInitialize(WorldObject* obj, AreaTriggerEntry const* at)
3531{
3532 if (obj)//handle object based scripts
3533 {
3534 switch (obj->GetTypeId())

3536 case TYPEID_UNIT:
3537 mScriptType = SMART_SCRIPT_TYPE_CREATURE;
3538 me = obj->ToCreature();

3540 break;
3541 case TYPEID_GAMEOBJECT:
3542 mScriptType = SMART_SCRIPT_TYPE_GAMEOBJECT;
3543 go = obj->ToGameObject();
3544 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::OnInitialize: source is GameObject %u", go->GetEntry());

3547 TC_LOG_ERROR("misc", "SmartScript::OnInitialize: Unhandled TypeID !WARNING!");

3551 {
3552 mScriptType = SMART_SCRIPT_TYPE_AREATRIGGER;
3553 trigger = at;
3554 TC_LOG_DEBUG("scripts.ai", "SmartScript::OnInitialize: source is AreaTrigger %u", trigger->ID);
3555 }
3556 else
3557 {
3558 TC_LOG_ERROR("misc", "SmartScript::OnInitialize: !WARNING! Initialized objects are NULL.");
3559 return;
3560 }
3561
3562 GetScript();//load copy of script
3563
3564 for (SmartAIEventList::iterator i = mEvents.begin(); i != mEvents.end(); ++i)
3565 InitTimer((*i));//calculate timers for first time use
3566
3567 ProcessEventsFor(SMART_EVENT_AI_INIT);
3568 InstallEvents();
3569 ProcessEventsFor(SMART_EVENT_JUST_CREATED);
3570}

3677void SmartScript::SetScript9(SmartScriptHolder& e, uint32 entry)
3678{
3679 //do NOT clear mTimedActionList if it's being iterated because it will invalidate the iterator and delete
3680 // any SmartScriptHolder contained like the "e" parameter passed to this function
3681 if (isProcessingTimedActionList)
3682 {
3683 TC_LOG_ERROR("scripts.ai", "Entry " SI64FMTD " SourceType %u Event %u Action %u is trying to overwrite timed action list from a timed action, this is not allowed!.", e.entryOrGuid, e.GetScriptType(), e.GetEventType(), e.GetActionType());
3684 return;
3685 }
3686
3687 mTimedActionList.clear();
3688 mTimedActionList = sSmartScriptMgr->GetScript(entry, SMART_SCRIPT_TYPE_TIMED_ACTIONLIST);
3689 if (mTimedActionList.empty())
3690 return;
3691 for (SmartAIEventList::iterator i = mTimedActionList.begin(); i != mTimedActionList.end(); ++i)
3692 {
3693 i->enableTimed = i == mTimedActionList.begin();//enable processing only for the first action
3694
3695 if (e.action.timedActionList.timerType == 0)
3696 i->event.type = SMART_EVENT_UPDATE_OOC;
3697 else if (e.action.timedActionList.timerType == 1)
3698 i->event.type = SMART_EVENT_UPDATE_IC;
3699 else if (e.action.timedActionList.timerType > 1)
3700 i->event.type = SMART_EVENT_UPDATE;
3701
3702 InitTimer((*i));
3703 }
3704}
